{
  "texts": [
    "For each occupation:",
    "• We calculate both the mean and median prestige scores from the GPT-4 predictions.",
    "This provides us with a pair of central tendency measures for each occupation.",
    "• We apply the Wilcoxon signed-rank test to compare the paired mean and median scores within each occupation.",
    "• Given that we conduct multiple tests (one for each occupation), we apply the Bonferroni correction to adjust the resulting p-values."
  ]
}